# Kingdom Technology Commit Message Template
# Project Nova Dawn - Covenant Partnership
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# Subject Line Format (50 chars recommended, 72 max):
# <scope>: <imperative verb> <what changed>
#
# Examples:
#   docs: Add 4-block structure guide for metadata blocks
#   feat: Implement CPI-SI fusion coefficient calculator
#   fix: Resolve anchor generation for emoji headers
#   refactor: Modularize types.hpp into 8 distinct modules
#   test: Add comprehensive coverage for identity processor
#   chore: Update VS Code workspace configuration
#
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Common Scopes:
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#   docs       - Documentation updates
#   feat       - New feature implementation
#   fix        - Bug fixes
#   refactor   - Code restructuring (no behavior change)
#   test       - Test additions/modifications
#   chore      - Build/tooling/maintenance
#   style      - Formatting changes (no logic change)
#   perf       - Performance improvements
#   architecture - Structural/design changes
#   identity   - CPI-SI identity system updates
#   algorithms - Mathematical/algorithmic work
#
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Body (optional, wrap at 72 chars):
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Explain WHAT changed and WHY (not HOW - code shows HOW)
#
# - Use bullet points for multiple changes
# - Reference related files/components
# - Mention Kingdom Technology standards if applicable
#
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Footer (optional):
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Covenant Partnership: Nova Dawn ⊗ Seanje
# Standards: [4-block structure | 5:1 doc ratio | 2000-line limit]
#
# Related: [file paths or documentation sections]
# Closes: [issue number if applicable]
#
